# Olympics API
Olympics API is a simple API, allowing one to gather information on particular entities of the Olympics Games.

# Group Olympics
Resources of the **Olympics API**

## Olympics Collection [/scrape/olympics]
A list of all olympic games

### List all Olympic Games [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "0":{
                "id":       Olympics_ID_as_int,
                "year":     "Year_as_int,
                "season":   "Season type (Summer/Winter)",
                "city"      "Host City Name",
                "country":  "Host Country Name",
                "events":   [
                                {
                                    "id":       "Event_ID",
                                    "name":     "Event Name",
                                    "sport":    "Sport Name"
                                }
                            ]
            }
        }
        
## Olympics [/scrape/olympics/{id}]
A single olympic games with all its details

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Olympics desired. Has example value.

